::Shredder::

Shredder barks a short laugh as Quickstrike goes into stasis lock.

"Pathetic fuzor," he mumbles as he grabs the fuzor by the leg, turning to 
walk off.

"You stay here," he says to Scorponok as he walks off toward the CR chambers, 
dragging Quickstrike behind him.
